Amp it Up from Founders Hub works on top of LinkedIn to grow your network, add value to the community and help spread high-value content.

The plugin allows you to easily connect with other Founders Hub members and highlights quality content from them so you can share it with your followers.

It helps community members to amplify their voice and allows you to harness that power to reach a larger audience yourself.

Simply connect your LinkedIn profile, install the plugin, connect with members and engage with the highlighted posts on your LinkedIn feed.
